# [Interview #972: AMOL Signing Report - JaimieKrycho, Entry #34](https://www.theoryland.com/intvmain.php?i=972#34)

#### Question

Do Jenn Aiel still exist at the time of the book?

#### Brandon Sanderson

There might be some Jenn Aiel still around.
